,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMemento 主要玩雙時間線<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇到呢個笑左</blockquote><br />\n有咩錯，廢時劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面果堆都講緊出戲個主題<br />\n去到momento變左敍事方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我個人好鍾意momento，覺得正過interstellar同inception <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6e50647be8f068796096c70dffdbebf1890cc6","tid":105740,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>羔羊代表咩，尖叫係咩意思？對Starling有咩影響？對故事推進有咩幫助？<br />\nDr. Lecter問黎做咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女主角童年夢魘<br />\n細個睇到班羊喺到尖叫但救唔到 變相令佢大個想做fbi</blockquote><br />\n有印象，但好似唔係咁特別，唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初頭 expect silence of the lambs 加埋張poster 係有特別意思，例如 女主角既黑暗面 呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08db07d37c1b03007fa3015f00958527eec22c9","tid":105740,"uid":73281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:36:38.000Z","msg":"重睇過幾次都係覺得好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而覺得美劇Hannibal正到hihi"},{"pid":"b0cd1f089f59b62ac2bb863184f98771cadd474d","tid":105740,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重睇過幾次都係覺得好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而覺得美劇Hannibal正到hihi</blockquote><br />\n唔明點解拎到Oscar，可能同年既電影質素低"},{"pid":"3fe1dfb5c0b7556b926c0097055b52bf27a1cfef","tid":105740,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMemento 主要玩雙時間線<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇到呢個笑左</blockquote><br />\n有咩錯，廢時劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面果堆都講緊出戲個主題<br />\n去到momento變左敍事方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我個人好鍾意momento，覺得正過interstellar同inception <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為對上睇都好耐，隱約記得故仔唔算特別，最正係睇落散亂既拍攝手法，令觀眾男主視角同步而感到記憶錯亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ninterstellar 講親情超越時間空間都幾感動既，Inception 我都幾鍾意個設定，<br />\n兩套我都係戲院睇，睇Interstellar 好似欣賞緊藝術片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c557a7fe1176ce2e579bb7a53cc853982abc73","tid":105740,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"紅龍，殺機好似都唔錯？"},{"pid":"4ae84e3fc3e47e23e8bfd2f28e188de1f35f7a58","tid":105740,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c9bb0c259e330b3418f187cbbccf2e65c5c92b8","tid":105740,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2e0b2919f8921a5fdf0423c52c2d9301c2ed50b","tid":105740,"uid":24593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb8ab55ea570c074f7c071589aeb485ed6e29a5","tid":105740,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Jodie Foster 同 Anthony Hopkins 演技精湛唔駛多講<br />\n鏡頭運用出色，氣氛營造都好<br />\n但撇除呢d外在因素後，故事劇情本身有冇咩值得咁高好評既原因？或者可以令人細思、發人深省既地方？<br />\nGoogle完好多影評都冇講，我自己睇完覺得：吓，咁咋？故事性唔太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知咩叫character study？<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">有所謂主題就叫好戲</span>，咁the island, in time呢啲科幻片都係經典啦<br />\n最重要係執行得好唔好吖嘛！</blockquote><br />\n我冇講過<br />\n我係指出佳作有值得細味既地方 =/= 有主題就係佳作<br />\n<br />\n我唔識character study，但人地叫我介紹Silence of the lambs既話<br />\n我只能講欣賞演技，因為我講唔出內容好睇之處"},{"pid":"1edfe066d8af58ff615105c04624b9e240fcd67b","tid":105740,"uid":44895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Jodie Foster 同 Anthony Hopkins 演技精湛唔駛多講<br />\n鏡頭運用出色，氣氛營造都好<br />\n但撇除呢d外在因素後，故事劇情本身有冇咩值得咁高好評既原因？或者可以令人細思、發人深省既地方？<br />\nGoogle完好多影評都冇講，我自己睇完覺得：吓，咁咋？故事性唔太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早嗰排睇完，完全同意你嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5be4215e505c069334fa2fafc0a17f25521618","tid":105740,"uid":58101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d62be990707605cc86ea06e4ef78c30fef4eb48c","tid":105740,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"好簡單，因為而家睇同當年睇係唔同<br />\n劇情黎講，以現今既眼光睇係平凡、老套，非常行貨。但當年黎講雖然咁樣既情節唔算創新，但絕對唔差，而且引人入勝，加上演技爐火純青，無得輸"},{"pid":"63c22b36380de144110c54572c7f063bb907f4d4","tid":105740,"uid":18720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"antoney hopkins啲演技簡直係同daniel day lewis同tom hanks不相伯仲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果睇羔羊唔夠喉 我極強烈建議睇埋westworld<br />\nwestworld本身係套有今生冇來世既劇<br />\n但dr.ford真係好戲到要瘋狂番j佢啲片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇佢做戲係至高無上既享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"